%F A004152 Conjecture (heuristic, from Stirling's formula and A027868): a(n) = c1 * n * log n - (c1 + 9/8) * n + O(log n), with c1 = 9 / (2*log(10)). - _Mike Sheppard_, Sep 21 2025
%e A004152 a(5) = 3 because 5! = 120 and 1 + 2 + 0 = 3.
